{"type":"user","uuid":"e4eda85d-d5ee-43ac-a5b2-c9ef4c1f527f","session_id":"7bf91201-6528-470c-bfa4-e2217c84d56d","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"019cde4accc861fc89da02f55190ac13","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1вҶ’DOC_LEVEL: L1\n   2вҶ’MODULE: runtime\n   3вҶ’PATH: src/**\n   4вҶ’DESCRIPTION: telegram + web request handling + sessioned CodeBuddy bridge\n   5вҶ’\n   6вҶ’ENTRYPOINT:\n   7вҶ’- src/index.js -> createHttpServer + optional Telegram bot launch\n   8вҶ’\n   9вҶ’KEY_FILES:\n  10вҶ’- src/config.js\n  11вҶ’- src/http/server.js\n  12вҶ’- src/routes/api-routes.js\n  13вҶ’- src/services/chat-service.js\n  14вҶ’- src/services/pipeline-control-service.js\n  15вҶ’- src/pipeline-infra/config-loader.js\n  16вҶ’- src/pipeline-infra/script-runner.js\n  17вҶ’- src/adapters/codebuddy.js\n  18вҶ’- src/bot/telegram.js\n  19вҶ’- src/services/system-exec-service.js\n  20вҶ’\n  21вҶ’SUBDIRS:\n  22вҶ’- src/adapters -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/adapters.prizm\n  23вҶ’- src/bot -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/bot.prizm\n  24вҶ’- src/http -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/http.prizm\n  25вҶ’- src/routes -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/routes.prizm\n  26вҶ’- src/security -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/security.prizm\n  27вҶ’- src/services -> .prizm-docs/runtime/services.prizm\n  28вҶ’- src/pipeline-infra -> .prizm-docs/runtime/pipeline-infra.prizm\n  29вҶ’- src/utils -> (lazy) .prizm-docs/runtime/utils.prizm\n  30вҶ’\n  31вҶ’INTERFACES:\n  32вҶ’- HTTP: /healthz, /api/events(SSE), /api/chat, /api/chat/reset, /api/screenshot, /api/system/exec\n  33вҶ’- Telegram: /start, /help, /reset, /screenshot, /exec, /pipeline, /bugfix, /planner, /status, /logs, /stop, text message relay\n  34вҶ’\n  35вҶ’TRAPS:\n  36вҶ’- ENABLE_TELEGRAM=true requires TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\n  37вҶ’- system exec is disabled unless ENABLE_SYSTEM_EXEC=true\n  38вҶ’- system exec requires ALLOWED_COMMAND_PREFIXES whitelist\n  39вҶ’- chat is serialized per session via chat-queue\n  40вҶ’\n  41вҶ’DECISIONS:\n  42вҶ’- 2026-03-09 | runtime-doc-init | model first-pass runtime map from source + API surface\n  43вҶ’- 2026-03-10 | runtime-infra-f001 | expose pipeline infra config in src/config.js and pipeline-control-service API for feature/bugfix run/status/stop/retry/logs/reset\n  44вҶ’- 2026-03-12 | runtime-f002 | add command routing layer for pipeline commands (/pipeline, /bugfix, /planner, /status, /logs, /stop)\n  45вҶ’"}],"is_error":false}],"role":"user"},"parent_tool_use_id":"019cde4a927cad823de88d83a3b65383","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T19:06:11.564Z","_requestId":"d5751c68510146c3a3ea5dbb4d6e54b2"}
